@startuml
[*] --> Idle : Create Session

Idle --> Active : Connect User & Psychologist

Active --> Paused : User requests pause
Paused --> Active : Resume

Active --> Critical : Risk detected (Observer triggered)
Critical --> Active : Risk resolved by Moderator
Critical --> Terminated : Emergency services called

Active --> Completed : Time limit reached / Manual end
Completed --> [*]

Terminated --> [*]

note right of Critical
    В этом состоянии активируются
    наблюдатели: Moderators,
    Emergency Services
end note
@enduml
